  <summary date="2021-05-20T15:09:09Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protecting Life in Health Savings Accounts Act

This bill prohibits payment of expenses from specified tax-exempt savings accounts, including health savings accounts and health flexible spending arrangements and reimbursement arrangements, for abortions, except for abortions to end a pregnancy due to rape or incest or to protect the life or health of the mother.</summary>
